            <title>[AMQ-6055] SASL PLAIN auth with AMQP doesn&apos;t take authzid into account</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6055</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SASL PLAIN authentication with AMQP doesn&apos;t take authzid into account and fails authentication when it&apos;s fully legal in SASL PLAIN.&lt;/p&gt;

