&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6055&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6055&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Account for Authzid in SASL PLAIN mechanism and provide a means to fail&lt;br/&gt;
the authorization if the challenge response is invalid.  Update the&lt;br/&gt;
client to properly exclude sasl mechanism that don&apos;t apply to it&apos;s&lt;br/&gt;
configured credentials such as using only ANONYMOUS when no user or&lt;br/&gt;
password is set.  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
